text: Rail Corridor access path (informal) at Blk1010 Alexandra Village Industrial Estate is now paved with cement.

Written in March 2024
The entrance to the Rail Corridor (also known as the Green Corridor or Greenway).

It was recently renovated.

It wasn't paved before and often became muddy after rain, but I'm grateful that it's been cleaned up.

I'll take this opportunity to post a photo from before.
